                <mxCell id="examples_text" value="Personnel Class: &#39;Widget Assembly Operator&#39;&#xa;Personnel Class Property: &#39;Class 1 Certified&#39; (values: True/False)&#xa;Person: &#39;Jane Smith&#39; (ID: EMP001)&#xa;Person Property: &#39;Class 1 Certified&#39; = True&#xa;&#xa;Composition Note: Deleting a Personnel Class requires deleting all its properties. Deleting a Person requires deleting all its properties. Enforce at application layer since TypeDB doesn&#39;t support native cascading deletes." style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontSize=10;fillColor=none;strokeColor=none;" parent="1" vertex="1">
